{"tid":625221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全城搶居屋】疑似喇嘛樂富交表 穿名牌波鞋惹熱議","createTime":"2018-04-11T09:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T23:29:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"06680439487255b626082af3ea59a364bd096fe1","tid":625221,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】新一期居今晚正式截止交表，不少申請者作最後衝刺，帶齊文件到房委會樂富中心交表。有網民昨見到一名疑似喇嘛到場交表格，並稱有專人帶隊，引起網民討論。<br />\n<br />\n有網民於Facebook專頁「巴打絲打」上載圖片，網民指昨日到房委會樂富中心遞交新居屋申請表格時，見到一名疑似喇嘛到場交表，「點知而家連喇嘛都去抽屋，仲有專人帶隊」圖片所見，該名疑似喇嘛穿有名牌波鞋，並揹上新潮斜揹袋。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都慨嘆僧多粥少，又指該名喇嘛身份可疑，「職業來的，睇開啲啦」、「睇佢對鞋都唔惹少」、「有錢高僧搶港樓，僧多粥少」、「 喇嘛唔係住佛寺嘅咩，住乜野居屋呀」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8o9j5Gs9HpBylWsdr_94HQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180411a112314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8o9j5Gs9HpBylWsdr_94HQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180411a112314.jpg&h=b2bb68d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E6%90%B6%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B-%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E5%96%87%E5%98%9B%E6%A8%82%E5%AF%8C%E4%BA%A4%E8%A1%A8-%E7%A9%BF%E5%90%8D%E7%89%8C%E6%B3%A2%E9%9E%8B%E6%83%B9%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-032500072.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%2590%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E5%2596%2587%25E5%2598%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25AF%258C%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E8%25A1%25A8-%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2589%258C%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E9%259E%258B%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25AD%25B0-032500072.html&d=9Q56bAYsZhWDnGmmLrhNDsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c8c788fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E6%90%B6%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B-%E7%96%91%E4%BC